<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Option 1 - Fixed Sidebar</title>
  <style>
    /* Basic reset */
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      display: flex;
      min-height: 100vh;
      color: #333;
    }

    .sidebar {
      width: 220px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-right: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .sidebar .logo-container {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .sidebar .logo-container img {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      cursor: pointer;
    }

    .sidebar nav ul {
      list-style: none;
    }

    .sidebar nav ul li {
      margin: 12px 0;
    }

    .sidebar nav ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .sidebar nav ul li a:hover {
      color: #007bff;
    }

    .content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .content h1 {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }

    .content p {
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      max-width: 800px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <!-- Fixed sidebar container -->
  <div class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo-container">
      <!-- Link to TPA Home -->
      <a href="https://thepocusatlas.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="../images/vexus-ai-logo.png" alt="Vexus-AI: Go to TPA Home" />
      </a>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 1</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 2</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Menu Item 3</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <!-- Main content area -->
  <div class="content">
    <h1>Option 1: Fixed Sidebar Demo</h1>
    <p>This is a simple demonstration of a fixed sidebar layout. The Vexus-AI logo at the top links back to The POCUS Atlas (TPA Home). Additional menu items are placed just below the logo.</p>
    <p>In a real project, you can adjust colors, fonts, spacing, and add any further UI elements you need.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
